ActNational Defence Act
PrecisAmendments to the QUEEN'S REGULATIONS AND ORDERS FOR THE CANADIAN FORCES by defining full-time service for members of the Reserve Force serving on an operation (Article 9.075) and by amending the meaning of Class "C" Reserve Service to include full-time service on military operations (Article 9.08).
